{"tid":686031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地產經紀爭客開拖 4對1打到瞓地踢頭","createTime":"2018-06-01T02:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T03:37:07.000Z","uid":148652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0373008c87c9bcd082714b2b383a0f82e3974fd1","tid":686031,"uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/102330_98dde4d5cca719c4840ca5454ff05132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F102330_98dde4d5cca719c4840ca5454ff05132.jpg&h=a0054b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵食艱難同行如敵國，荃灣有地產經紀疑為爭客大打交。有市民拍攝到一段短片，顯示大埔白石角新盤嘉熙，在荃灣沙咀道嘉達環球中心售樓處外，有地產經紀疑為爭生意毆鬥。片中一名穿白衫男子，遭3名黑衫及1名白衫男子追打，事主無力反抗，被推埋牆後，再遭4人揮拳圍毆，事主被打到瞓地。。<br />\n<br />\n不過4人未肯收手，有人起腳狂踢，事主以雙手護頭，施襲者中以白衫男最狼，在場其他人士，未敢施援及阻止。其後一名穿粉紅色衫男子衝前制止，4人方肯罷休，而事主則倒臥地上，未知傷勢如何。"},{"pid":"7ce763ccb6a7251da3fecda31856498f4b3f57e1","tid":686031,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab3ddc895b6c0c082b7b7d0e26082bfa1025caa","tid":686031,"uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:48:52.000Z","msg":"鐘意打交既你一定要加入地產界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c0bb86fd2f9198e9beedf11a40a06f64556d30","tid":686031,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:16:58.000Z","msg":"LF2"},{"pid":"d70b98abd94566521f349973bf4ac4c0da8b99e6","tid":686031,"uid":72480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"搞返個地產界金牌打手選拔賽啦"},{"pid":"f006342892f3022e2291bf2091cacdfae9d50144","tid":686031,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 地產狗"},{"pid":"dc8838ebd32793ce94241ddc908cc0c042ee4d51","tid":686031,"uid":6562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"地產霸拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b984d0b24e72f88ff0fc4bd834b13c6c076f6013","tid":686031,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:35:39.000Z","msg":"扮客，叫佢地打，邊個打贏幫襯邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659fe3841168fcca54aa09427690e8a8c8301b9c","tid":686031,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}